WEBVTT

00:05.588 --> 00:07.757
(sighs)

00:07.841 --> 00:09.300
Morning.

00:09.384 --> 00:10.552
{\an1}Morning.

00:10.635 --> 00:11.761
You slept in.

00:11.845 --> 00:14.097
I'm just tossing
and turning all night.

00:14.180 --> 00:17.267
I haven't had a good night's
sleep since Joey left.

00:17.350 --> 00:18.184
Oh, he'll turn up.

00:18.268 --> 00:20.520
I thought
you were sleeping at Steve's.

00:20.603 --> 00:22.147
That was the plan.

00:22.230 --> 00:23.648
What happened?

00:23.732 --> 00:26.609
Oh, nothing out
of the ordinary.

00:26.693 --> 00:28.486
I don't know.
Maybe Steve's right.

00:28.570 --> 00:30.989
Maybe I am the one
with the hormone imbalance.

00:31.072 --> 00:33.658
Otherwise, why would I keep
trying to change

00:33.742 --> 00:35.410
{\an3}what obviously
cannot be changed?

00:35.493 --> 00:36.411
(scoffs)

00:36.494 --> 00:37.787
Are things really that bad?

00:37.871 --> 00:39.164
{\an1}He's just

00:39.247 --> 00:41.416
so insensitive, you know?

00:41.499 --> 00:42.625
About what?
Everything.

00:42.709 --> 00:44.085
Sex.

00:44.169 --> 00:46.087
Last night,
he actually demanded his quota.

00:46.171 --> 00:47.464
{\an3}Well, boys

00:47.547 --> 00:48.923
{\an1}will be boys.
Yeah.

00:49.007 --> 00:50.633
{\an1}Did you talk to him?
Yeah.

00:50.717 --> 00:51.968
He pouted.

00:52.051 --> 00:53.219
I hate that.

00:53.303 --> 00:54.929
{\an1}He didn't say anything?
Oh, yeah, he did.

00:55.013 --> 00:56.222
Here's a quote.

00:56.306 --> 00:57.974
"Gee, Clare, what's wrong?

00:58.057 --> 00:59.976
Is it puffy, mean
and snappy time?"

01:00.059 --> 01:01.311
It's KEG-speak

01:01.394 --> 01:02.312
{\an1}for PMS.

01:02.395 --> 01:03.271
That's low.

01:03.354 --> 01:04.313
{\an1}Well, maybe
it's time

01:04.397 --> 01:06.483
I sink to his level.

01:06.566 --> 01:09.360
I think I know how to do it.

01:10.945 --> 01:12.989
Clare...

01:16.409 --> 01:18.828
{\an3}I gotta go; I'm gonna
be late for class.

01:18.912 --> 01:20.330
{\an6}Okay.
Thanks for
letting me vent.

01:20.413 --> 01:21.790
Be good.

01:21.873 --> 01:23.792
I will.

01:23.875 --> 01:25.919
Hello.

01:29.547 --> 01:31.299
Joey?

01:31.382 --> 01:32.467
{\an3}Hi.

01:32.550 --> 01:34.636
{\an1}Oh, my God, I've been
worried about you.

01:34.719 --> 01:36.221
Are you okay?

01:36.304 --> 01:38.223
I couldn't stay
at that stupid shelter.

01:38.306 --> 01:41.017
You don't have to; it's....
I'm not going back there.

01:41.100 --> 01:43.186
{\an3}Please, you can't
send me back there.

01:43.269 --> 01:44.604
You've got to promise.

01:44.687 --> 01:46.147
Okay, okay, I promise.

01:46.231 --> 01:48.233
Come here. It's okay.

01:51.778 --> 01:54.197
